{"words":[{"word":"i've","count":3},{"word":"help","count":2},{"word":"time","count":2},{"word":"waiting","count":2},{"word":"finally","count":2},{"word":"t-thanks","count":1},{"word":"okay","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"rover","count":1},{"word":"hero","count":1},{"word":"fought","count":1},{"word":"threnodian","count":1},{"word":"resolved","count":1},{"word":"crisis","count":1},{"word":"madam","count":1},{"word":"magistrate","count":1},{"word":"everyone's","count":1},{"word":"talking","count":1},{"word":"lady","count":1},{"word":"changli","count":1},{"word":"i-i","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"i'd","count":1},{"word":"chance","count":1},{"word":"person","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"would've","count":1},{"word":"goner","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"die","count":1},{"word":"someone","count":1},{"word":"found","count":1},{"word":"ugh","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"mt","count":1},{"word":"firmament's","count":1},{"word":"legend","count":1},{"word":"came","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"secret","count":1},{"word":"mountain","count":1},{"word":"half","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"going","count":1},{"word":"smoothly","count":1},{"word":"monsters","count":1},{"word":"pounced","count":1},{"word":"cough","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"fuling","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"T-Thanks for your help...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"I... I'm okay. Wait, you... Are you THE Rover...?","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"You're that hero who fought against the Threnodian, and you also resolved the time crisis here with Madam Magistrate. Everyone's been talking about you...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"And Lady Changli... I-I never thought I'd have the chance to see you in person...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"...Without your help, I would've been a goner for sure...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"I can't die here. Not when I've got someone waiting for me...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"I've finally, finally found it... After all this time... Ugh...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"I, I heard about Mt. Firmament's legend... So I came to find its secret...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"I've only been in the mountain for half a day, everything was going smoothly before those monsters pounced on me on my way back... *cough*...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035},{"text":"I must get back... Fuling... She's still waiting for me...","quest_name":"Immortal Blaze","quest_id":121000035}]}